advancement criteria

	time at previous status
	payment of gold
	ownership of artifact


benefits of title

	monthly income
	special report
	appoint other titles
	combat rating bonus


lord
	any noble may claim this title

knight
	requires a noble to have been lord for one year
	or, appointment by a king
	or, payment of 1,000 gold

baron
	requires knight to be owner of a castle


viscount
earl
	must be a baron
	appointment by king
	or one year as baron

